---
title: Mixed Bean and Veggie Panzanella Salad with a Lemon Vinaigrette
description: Crusty ciabatta is tossed with italian seasoning , shredded carrots, and a rich and meaty mixed beans. It's our light summery take on a hearty italian bean salad!
